<header class="banner-home">
  <div class="banner-home-polygon">
  </div>
  <div class="banner-home-heading">
    <h1>Local Help</h1>
    <h3>Help each other out</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="home-search-box">
    <%= render "shared/search_form" %>
  </div>
  <div class="banner-home-quote-position">
    <div class="banner-home-quote">
      <p class="banner-home-first-paragraph">
        Local Help is a community-driven task exchange. We connect people who could use a hand with someone nearby who can help them get it done.
      </p>
      <p class="banner-home-second-paragraph">
        Find someone in your area to help you with home repairs, shopping trips, or anything else you might need.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <svg class="arrows">
      <path class="a1" d="M0 0 L30 32 L60 0"></path>
      <path class="a2" d="M0 20 L30 52 L60 20"></path>
      <path class="a3" d="M0 40 L30 72 L60 40"></path>
  </svg>
</header>

<div class="banner-home-second-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="d-flex">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-7 col-xl-7 banner-home-left-side">
          <h1>Local Help explained</h1>
          <p>Whether you need someone to help you assemble some furniture, build your garden, or even just a friendly voice to talk you through getting your printer back up and running, Local Help has a wide range of top-rated volunteers to help you solve any issue. We also have paid tasks too, so you can support your community members and make a new friend in the process.</p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-around">
            <%= link_to 'See available tasks', tasks_path, class: 'btn-gradient' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-5 col-xl-5">
              <p>Add card here</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="banner-home-third-section">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1>How does it work?</h1>
      <p>With your Local Help account, you can list your issue or apply to help someone out. Manage all your messages in our built-in dashboard!</p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-around">
        <div class="banner-home-card" style="width: 20rem;">
          <div class="banner-home-card-polygon">
            <div class="banner-home-card-polygon">
              <h5>Create a new task</h5>
            </div>
            <p>Two to three sentences to explain how to create a task and why.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="banner-home-card" style="width: 20rem;">
          <div class="banner-home-card-polygon">
            <div class="banner-home-card-polygon">
              <h5>Apply for a task</h5>
            </div>
            <p>Two to three sentences to explain how to apply and why.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-around">
        <%= link_to 'Sign up for free', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn-gradient' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
